FBIS4-3532 "drchi078_a_94007" FBIS-CHI-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Ni Zhifu Meets World Trade Union Leader Ni Zhifu Meets World Trade Union Leader OW2104125594 Beijing XINHUA in English 1243 GMT 21 Apr 94 OW2104125594 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 21 (XINHUA) -- Ni Zhifu, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of China's National People's Congress (NPC), met here today with a delegation of the World Federation of Trade Unions, and they exchanged opinions on issues of common interest. The two-member delegation, headed by the general secretary of the World Federation of Trade unions, A. Zharikov, began a visit to China on April 18 at the invitation of the All-China Federation of Trade Unions.
